title: Ministry Of Sound - Superstar DJs (2013) (FLAC) (AciDToX8)
description:
Ministry Of Sound - Superstar DJs (2013) 

            Funky, Club House, Tech, Progressive | Ministry Of Sound UK

               Lossless | FLAC | unmixed | 2013 | 03:50:57 | 1690 Mb


We kick off this epic 3CD album with a collection of Dance music's most in demand global icons featuring David Guetta, Swedish House Mafia, Deadmau5, Avicii and Calvin Harris, before delving deeper into disc 2 with an exclusive mix of the world's most renowned live acts; DJ Fresh, Chase & Status, Nero, Skrillex, and newcomers Disclosure all feature. Finally we end in true style with an almost mythological mix including Electronic music's most legendary artists such as The Chemical Brothers, Tiesto, Armin Van Buuren, Faithless and Daft Punk.
